[^AUTHOR: WILKINS, GEORGE.
TEXT: THE MISERIES OF INFORST MARIAGE.
AS IT IS NOW PLAYD BY HIS MAIESTIES SERUANTS.
(...)
BY GEORGE WILKINS.
LONDON
PRINTED FOR GEORGE VINCENT, AND ARE TO BE SOLD AT HIS SHOP IN 
WOODSTREET. 
1607.
