talking
about wiues.
   [$ (^But.^) $] Let your wiues agree of that after, will you first #
be
richly married? [$ (^All.^) $] How Butler: richly married?
   [$ (^But.^) $] Rich in beauty, rich in purse, riche in vertue,    #
riche in all
things. But (^Mum^) , Ile say nothing, I know of two or three rich
heyres. But (^Cargo^) , my fiddlestick cannot play without Rozen:    #
Auant.
   [$ (^went.^) $] Butler.  
